As a #masc #lesbian I’ve literally never worn makeup. I reached out to make up pro Sacha Harford and asked for advice on what I should do for a daytime no make up/make up look.
Products include @Dr.PAWPAW clear balm, @Dr. BRANDT Skincare No More Baggage, @trishmcevoy tubular mascara, @makeupforever redness corrector, HD skin hydra glow, Full coverage, @got2bUSA Clear mascara, Duck Plump Lip Gloss. This easy daytime no makeup /makeup look is great for any masc lesbian. Contact Sacha if you want a private tutorial, she’s Brooklyn- based but can also do zoom.
